                        <li>Data portability</li>
                        <li>Withdrawal of consent</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>To exercise these rights, please contact us using the information provided in the "Contact Us" section.</p>
                </section>
                
                <section>
                    <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
                    <p>Our website is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>
                </section>
                
                <section>
                    <h2>9. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
                    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.</p>
                </section>
                
                <section>
                    <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
                    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@pixelstop.com">privacy@pixelstop.com</a>.</p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

